{"id":10623,"date":"2024-11-14T06:16:18","date_gmt":"2024-11-14T06:16:18","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/sampreciousmetals.com\/?post_type=product&#038;p=10623"},"modified":"2026-01-15T08:13:01","modified_gmt":"2026-01-15T08:13:01","slug":"sam-horse-silver-bar","status":"publish","type":"product","link":"https:\/\/sampreciousmetals.com\/product\/sam-horse-silver-bar\/","title":{"rendered":"SAM Horse"},"content":{"rendered":"<h3>SAM Horse Silver Bar<\/h3>\n<p><em>Symbol of Motion. Force of Will.<\/em><\/p>\n<p>Unbridled and untamed, the SAM Horse represents a life in motion\u2014powerful, purposeful, and free. This signature minted bar by Sam Precious Metals captures the spirit of perseverance and elegance, drawing from one of nature\u2019s most enduring symbols of strength.<\/p>\n<p>Across cultures and time, the horse has stood as a companion to ambition\u2014a creature that charges forward, unwavering, eyes fixed on the horizon. This bar is a tribute to that spirit. It honors those who pursue success not with haste, but with resilience and grace. Those who rise, press on, and become more with every stride.<\/p>\n<p>Crafted in-house at Sam Precious Metals\u2019 refinery, this bar is refined to exacting standards and certified under UAE Good Delivery. Each bar is made from responsibly sourced silver, fully traceable and refined with integrity\u2014designed for those who value meaning as much as material.<\/p>\n<p>Whether kept as a lasting investment or offered as a gesture of motivation, the SAM Horse is a reminder that when purpose meets persistence, no journey is too far.<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p>Available for purchase in rectangle, coin, pendant, and oval designs. With 999.9 purity level in 1 gram, 2.5 grams, 5 grams, 10 grams, 20 grams, 50 grams, 100 grams, \u00bd oz, and 1 oz sizes.<\/p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">SILVER 999<\/h3>\n<table>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>RECTANGLE<\/th>\n<th>COIN\/CIRCLE<\/th>\n<th>PENDANT<\/th>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: